title: Two sets of twins are born on the SAME DAY
text: show ad Two sets of twins are born on the SAME DAY as they defy 4.5million-to-one odds... and they have five other siblings (plus another one on the way!) Erin and Leah Sullivan were born on January 26 2016, the same date as twins Charlotte and Isabelle in 2008 Full-time mum Zoe was taken to Raigmore hospital, Inverness, for an emergency c-section last month On their birthdays, parents Ben and Zoe bought them lots of cupcakes instead of getting one cake Published: 01:00 GMT, 19 February 2017 | Updated: 01:42 GMT, 19 February 2017 7 shares
